---
title: Chorizo Meatball Bowls with Cilantro-Lime Rice and DIY Pico De Gallo
description: Savoury chorizo is combined with Mexican spices, crushed crispy shallots and jalapeños for these Tex-Mex-inspired meatballs. Lime sour cream and do-it-yourself pico de gallo are the perfect toppings to take your tastebuds to a bold flavour fiesta!
